            <title>[LU-4577] Dropped messages are not accounted correctly</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4577</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;LNET messages that are dropped are not accounted for correctly in /proc/sys/lnet/stats&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;What I assume to be a simple typo is causing drop_length to be double-counted and drop_count to never be incremented.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Patch will be uploaded to Gerrit shortly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
